The '''Archery''' is a building in the [[Levy Barracks]] category. It is used to recruit [[Crossbowman|Crossbowmen]].

== Production ==
The Archery produces one [[Crossbowman]] every 15 seconds. It consumes 10 [[Wheat]] and 8 [[Gold]] per cycle.

